Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn@黑体\frz-90\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(420,415.5)}那样不是很酷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn@黑体\frz-90\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1287.499,415.5)}嗯 是很酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn@黑体\frz-90\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(864,443.499)}而且也不会\N给谁添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn@黑体\frz-90\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(55.5,590.999)}不过 那样不会\N让保安公司的信誉\N一落千丈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn@黑体\frz-90\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1731.495,970.999)\fad(0,300)}啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn@黑体\frz-90\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(879.501,890.999)\fad(0,300)}而且银行的信誉\N也会下降的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn@黑体\frz-90\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(111.501,874.999)\fad(0,300)}本来 这在现实中\N是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:17.17,cn,,0,0,0,,竟然会发生这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:19.84,cn,,0,0,0,,我不会让你碰到优梨糖一根手指头的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.84,0:24:21.53,cn,,0,0,0,,平丸先生那里也出事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.71,0:24:23.71,cn,,0,0,0,,下回  模仿与无意识
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.91,0:24:26.73,Secondary,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,66)\fs54}有梦想的话 什么样的困难都能克服
